Description:Test puzzle for replaying a copied-token untap loop from the commander combo list: Kiki-Jiki, Mirror Breaker plus Village Bell-Ringer. Record one cycle by activating Kiki-Jiki targeting Village Bell-Ringer, then let the token untap your creatures. Repeat the recorded cycle until you have enough hasty Bell-Ringer tokens to attack for lethal damage.

